lead_paragraph: Morgan Stock came off the bench to hit 7 of 9 shots, including four 3-pointers, and scored 18 points, to lead No. 23 Missouri to a 79-64 win over No. 22 Florida on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Stock Lifts No. 23 Missouri Women Over No. 22 Florida 79-63
